/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_orderpackge */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_orderpackge (
PackID int identity(1,1),
PackgeCode nvarchar(50) not null,
OrderID int not null,
ExpressID int not null,
ExpCode nvarchar(100) null,
Money decimal(10,2) not null,
Num int not null,
Status int not null default 0,
IsPack bit null,
PackTime datetime not null default getdate(),
SendTime datetime null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
Description nvarchar(200) null,
Isexport int null,
IsCSVexport int null,
IsPrint int null,
constraint PK_BUSI_ORDERPACKGE primary key (PackID)
)
go
